Recursive binary search:
function binarySearch(arr, low, high, key):
  if high >= low:
    mid = (high + low) // 2
    if arr[mid] == key:
      return mid
    elif arr[mid] > key:
      return binarySearch(arr, low, mid - 1, key)
    else:
      return binarySearch(arr, mid + 1, high, key)
  else:
    return -1

Advantages: Simpler code.
